{"tid":2005021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟一致同意巴爾幹6國成新成員 抗衡中俄影響","createTime":"2020-05-07T00:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T01:11:42.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ad34138aa3549df201e9f427c6d5b9421a3fef","tid":2005021,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T00:14:35.000Z","msg":"歐盟27個成員國領袖周三在峰會上，一致支持6個巴爾幹半島國家成為歐盟新成員，並且給予6國更多財政援助，以抗衡俄羅斯與中國在區內的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n根據歐盟峰會會後公告，阿爾巴尼亞、波赫、科索沃、塞爾維亞、北馬其頓及蒙特內哥羅六個巴爾幹半島國家領袖，也參與今次峰會。<br />\n<br />\n同時，歐盟將向6國提供33億歐羅(280.8億港元)援助，協助應對新冠肺炎疫情。中國與俄羅斯已經派遣醫療隊到這些國家，協助應對疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2458528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2458528&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=0a9ff275\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2458528</a>"},{"pid":"448bdb50495b05e31f68f4eb8734bc1f0b8d5f34","tid":2005021,"uid":69157,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T00:15:42.000Z","msg":"塞爾維亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adead18c7536cc0c7c724e335912943533614e1","tid":2005021,"uid":357030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"448bdb50495b05e31f68f4eb8734bc1f0b8d5f34","tid":2005021,"uid":69157,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T00:15:42.000Z","msg":"塞爾維亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.